descriptionHtml:
Cadence is evolving the way people plan, experience, and remember events—no matter what shape or size ✨.

FOR ATTENDEES
Everything you need to make the most of your time and Experience Every Moment.
🔎 Find & review all the event details you need to know
📢 Stay up-to-date with important announcements & surprises
👀 See who's coming, connect, & stay in touch (for real this time)
💬 Conveniently chat 1:1 or in group channels
✨ Capture & share all the amazing moments in the Live Feed
😍 Relive your favorite moments from the events you attend
🗺️ Explore top spots & hidden gems in the area
➡️ Create your own event experiences for free! Cadence helps you plan and sprinkle some magic to events of any type, any size, anywhere.

WHY PEOPLE PREFER CADENCE
• "The look of a custom-designed app with none of the cost."
• "I haven't told my colleagues how easy Cadence is to use yet. I'm letting them think I'm a tech genius!"
• "It was so fun to see our attendees sharing photos documenting their travel to our Conference. It was as if the event had already started before they arrived!"
• "When you're organizing an event for 6,000+ people, things change all the time. We loved that we could edit the schedule, manage attendee groups, and send notifications straight from the app."
• "The Cadence team was incredibly responsive and helpful throughout the process, from set-up to event follow-up. It felt great to have them cheering us on remotely."

BENEFITS OF USING CADENCE
• Create beautiful & unforgettable event experiences directly in the Cadence app
• Easily make adjustments to all aspects of your event from the Cadence app
• Engage your audience with surveys, live polls, competitions, scavenger hunts, and more
• Control all event communications from the Cadence app
• Easily invite people by email or text
• Cadence automatically generates Moments—a sharable URL where attendees can view, download and share the events top Moments to relive the joys of the event for years to come.

IDEAL EVENT TYPES
• Conferences & Congresses
• Music, Food, & Arts Festivals
• Company Events
• Networking Events
• Group Travel & Tours
• Accelerators & Hackathons
• Fundraisers, Galas, & Awards
• Marketing & Product Launches
• School and Family Reunions
• Parties & Celebrations

**In-app demo events are available**

ESSENTIAL FEATURES
The features you need to create an unforgettable event. Looking for more? Check our website eventcadence.com
• Schedule
• Live Feed
• Profiles
• Explore
• Messaging
• Notifications

YOUR DEDICATED CUSTOMER SUCCESS MANAGER
Our customer success team will work with you every step of the way, from guiding you through the planning process to delivering an exceptional event experience.

MEETING WITH YOUR CUSTOMERS?
The Cadence Appointments feature is an organized and collaborative approach to meaningful customer engagement.

SMART SCHEDULING – Schedule around existing appointments, the event schedule, and internal meetings. Is another colleague also meeting with this customer? We’ll let you know.
CUSTOMER EMPOWERMENT – Personalized email outreach gives your customers the ability to choose the appointment date and time that works best for their schedule. Appointment options are updated in real-time based on internal availability.

ON-SITE CHECK-INS – Check-in options can be configured for reporting and compliance, including standard “tap to check-in”, signature capture, and opt-in/opt-out disclaimers for FMV.

CUSTOMER PROFILES – Quick access to your customer’s affiliation, bio, and contact information. Review a customer’s profile while onsite and be prepared for your meeting.

ENGAGEMENT HISTORY – We keep track of your previous engagements with each customer for informed future planning.
